1991;;Love Hurts;;American;;Bud Yorkin;;Jeff Daniels, Judith Ivey, Cloris Leachman;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Love_Hurts_(1991_film);;Paul Weaver (Jeff Daniels) is accustomed to playing around on his wife Nancy (Cynthia Sikes) from his baseball-playing days. When divorce papers are filed against him, Paul decides to travel to Pennsylvania and attend his sister's wedding. But Nancy and his two children are both there, making the situation uncomfortable for everyone.